    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The <ref refid="classSymCompartment" kindref="compound">SymCompartment</ref> class sets up a symmetric compartment for branched nerve calculations. Handles electronic structure and also channels. This version splits the Ra between either end of the compartment and is hence slightly cleaner than the asymmetric compartment. The default EE method is not a particularly efficient way of doing the calculations, so we should use a solver for any substantial calculations. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
